to catch cold or anything.
- All right.

597
00:43:11,256 --> 00:43:13,792
Um, I just wanted
to say, Robert,
if you ever need anything,

598
00:43:13,892 --> 00:43:16,728
anything at all, you just
come on over and ask.

599
00:43:16,828 --> 00:43:19,898
